The paper deals with the wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of feedback in enhancing secrecy capacity is a common theme in communication engineering (cs.CE) and signal processing (cs.MM). The paper also introduces a novel feedback technique, which could fall under the category of system and control (cs.SI).
